  <name>Encoding Explorer</name>
  <summary>Transform characters into binary</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Encoding Explorer is a tool for learning character encoding. Below are the main features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Encode characters to ASCII, UTF-8, UTF-16, and UTF-32.</li>
      <li>Encode numbers to IEEE-754 half, single, and double precision format.</li>
      <li>Supports real-time encoding.</li>
      <li>Change the endianness of a multi-byte encoding.</li>
      <li>Provides user-friendly interface for exploring encodings.</li>
      <li>Switch to light, dark, or system mode.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

